  <div class="card" style="padding:32px; margin-top:16px;">
    <p style="font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--xd-text-muted); margin-bottom:4px;">Usage</p>
    <p style="font-size:13px; color:var(--xd-text-muted); margin-bottom:0;">All form classes are theme-aware — they respond to the <code style="font-family:var(--xd-font-mono); font-size:12px; background:var(--xd-surface-2); padding:2px 6px; border-radius:5px;">data-theme</code> attribute automatically.</p>
